egr221a.interfaces.worklists

Class WorkList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • egr221a.interfaces.worklists.WorkList<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of elements in the worklist
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FIFOWorkList, LIFOWorkList, PriorityWorkList

    public abstract class WorkList<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<E>
    An object that stores work to be done in some specified order. This class should never be sub-classed directly. Further sub=classes indicate exactly how the elements should be handled.
    Version:
    SP 2017
    Author:
    Mikyung Han
